"fuel pods, we can greatly increase the range of an aircraft by loading more "
"fuel on board, and improve the craft's speed by allowing the engines enough "
"juice to run on maximum all the way. It also lets pilots make far more "
"liberal use of the afterburner, further upping the speed, allowing us to "
"better compete with hostile UFOs.\n"
"\n"
"Take note, however, that installing a fuel pod will add a significant amount "
"of weight to the craft. Care must be taken not to overload our airframes. If "
"an aircraft is too heavy to safely launch, our Command Centre computers will "
"automatically deny it launch clearance.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Recommended Doctrine\n"
"\n"
"We should make use of these pods in any situation where our aircraft are "
"unable to reach their destinations, or where they end up with too little "
"fuel to continue engaging a UFO, or where a large section of ground is left "
"uncovered by our network of bases. They will help to extend our reach and "
"provide more protection to Earth and our people.\n"
"\n"
