"separately due to the size differences, power levels and complexity of the "
"systems involved.\n"
"\n"
"Our notes on Continuous Wave Laser Operation have produced a lot of designs, "
"and this is possibly the most difficult one to bring into reality: a "
"deuterium-fluoride laser weapon the size of an ordinary pistol.\n"
"\n"
